data.description: Discover luxury living in this 2-bedroom, large townhouse located in the upscale Royal Palm Beach community. Ideal for modern lifestyles, this residence boasts a recently remodeled interior with a brand-new kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and upgraded bathrooms. The marble floors downstairs add an elegant touch, while the spacious family room provides a comfortable retreat.Convenience is key, with proximity to the Turnpike, shopping malls, and A-grade schools. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in your large fenced patio, perfect for entertaining or quiet relaxation. The community offers additional amenities, including a refreshing pool and a basketball court, enhancing your lifestyle. Experience the epitome of comfort and style in this meticulously maintained townhouse.
